data.description: This home has a brand new roof with a  30 year transferable warranty. This gorgeous home is hidden away and nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac in a one street subdivision. Beautiful landscaping gives this home awesome curb appeal. The home has an open floorplan for great family interaction and is perfect for entertaining. It features 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms in a split floor plan with lots of natural light and huge windows to let that light shine in. Wired for surround sound outside and in garage. Covered back patio with additional paved area for swing and a fire pit! Huge garage has a separate bonus storage area for tools and lawn equipment. Schedule your showing today!
